articles.title: Jujuboside A induces bladder cancer cell apoptosis by inhibiting ATP1A2-mediated mitochondrial energy metabolism regulation.
articles.summary: Jujuboside A, a natural compound, effectively triggers bladder cancer cell death by disrupting their energy production mechanism.

articles.title: Test: Breakthrough in Lung Cancer Treatment
articles.summary: A new targeted therapy successfully treated 60% of advanced lung cancer patients with specific genetic mutations, offering hope for improved outcomes.
